messages.messageBody:
Did anyone mention The King and I? The animated version of it was just on
Cartoon Netwrok the other day and my youngest son just LOVED it! :)

I was one of the lucky ones who got to see Yule Brenner as the King Live at
the Pantages theater in Los Angeles before he passed away! It was awesome!
One of my favorite musicals!

Oh yes, and another musical I wasn't sure I saw listed....Starlight Express!
Another one of my other favorites! I have seen it 4 times now since 1990 and
my boys have now seen it twice! :)

Just thought I would throw those in in case they were not mentioned! :)

Patti and the boys (Chris 13, Matthew 7, Anthony 6)
Life Long Learning Academy
